title: Tech Stocks to Watch: What Q3 Earnings Tell Us
description: Barron's senior managing editor Lauren R. Rublin and deputy editor Alex Eule discuss this week's raft of Big Tech earnings, from Facebook, Apple, Alphabet, and more, and what the numbers mean for the companies' stocks.
